		<article class="entry hentry author-jenny-lo post-type-text article-index-5" id="article-58d43aa286e6c04becf1ab10" data-item-id="58d43aa286e6c04becf1ab10">

			<p class="entry-categories">
				
			</p>
			<h1 data-content-field="title" class="entry-title">
				
					<a href="/teajournal/2017/3/23/tea-subscription-2016-december">Alishan: Tea Subscription 2016 December</a>
				
			</h1>

			<p class="entry-date-author">
				<span class="entry-author"><a href="/teajournal?author=54028563e4b09fa759f11482">Jenny Lo</a> · </span><time class="published" datetime="2017-03-23"><a href="/teajournal/2017/3/23/tea-subscription-2016-december">March 23, 2017</a></time>
			</p>

			<div class="entry-content">
				
					
						<div class="sqs-layout sqs-grid-12 columns-12" data-layout-label="Post Body" data-type="item" data-updated-on="1490303924890" id="item-58d43aa286e6c04becf1ab10"><div class="row sqs-row"><div class="col sqs-col-12 span-12"><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html" data-block-type="2" id="block-61baa32c27d34cbd04b9"><div class="sqs-block-content"><h3>Alishan: Tea Subscription 2016 December</h3><p>“A cup of tea would restore my normality."<br />[<em>Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy, Screenplay</em>]&nbsp;―<a href="http://www.goodreads.com/author/show/4.Douglas_Adams"> </a>Douglas Adams<a href="http://www.goodreads.com/author/show/4.Douglas_Adams"> </a></p></div></div><div class="sqs-block image-block sqs-block-image" data-block-type="5" id="block-yui_3_17_2_1_1490071600107_262900"><div class="sqs-block-content">








  

    
  
    <div
        class="
