			<h1 data-content-field="title" class="entry-title">
				
					<a href="/teajournal/2016/5/9/five-elements">Learn | 5 key elements to making good tea 五項關鍵影響茶的品質</a>
				
			</h1>

			<p class="entry-date-author">
				<span class="entry-author"><a href="/teajournal?author=54028563e4b09fa759f11482">Jenny Lo</a> · </span><time class="published" datetime="2016-08-28"><a href="/teajournal/2016/5/9/five-elements">August 28, 2016</a></time>
